title: Week 10 preview & Browns vs Ravens recap
itunes:title: Week 10 preview & Browns vs Ravens recap
description:
A room filled with heroes – Colleen Wolfe, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Gregg Rosenthal – go game-by-game recapping each week 10 matchup, and revealing which team is their “Lock of the Week”. Plus, the heroes recap the Thursday night game between the Browns and the Ravens.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
